    public class HASEL
extends RAkELd
    HASEL - Partitions labels into subsets based on the dataset defined hierarchy. Note: assuming that a . (fullstop/period) in the attribute names defines hierarchical branches, e.g., Europe.Spain.
    Version:
    June 2014
